OL,4,G2310F24 Hours in A&E
OL,5,     GThis episode meets patients whose
OL,6,     Gvisions of the world are rocked
OL,7,     Gby life-changing events. Sergio,
OL,8,     Gwho's 44, and Alan, who's 71,
OL,9,     Ghave both been badly injured in
OL,10,     Gcycling accidents.
OL,11,G0015F999: On the Front Line
OL,12,     GParamedics treat a woman with a
OL,13,     Gbroken leg, a man who's passed
OL,14,     Gout in the street, a woman who's
OL,15,     Ghad a seizure on a bus, and a man
OL,16,     Gwho's collapsed in his bathroom.
